import '@progress/kendo-theme-default/dist/all.css';
import Nav from '../components/nav'
import ChartContainer from '../components/chart-container'

const seriesData = [
    6000,
    3000,
    1500,
    2250,
    1500,
    3000,
    2250,
    1500,
    2250,
    1500,
    2250,
    2250,
    4500,
    7500,
    4500
];

const Chart = () => (
    <>
    <Nav/>
    <ChartContainer seriesData={seriesData} />
    </>
);

export default Chart;
